      @CheckReturnValue default String applicationId()
      Returns:

    • applicationIdAsLong

      @CheckReturnValue long applicationIdAsLong()
      Returns:
      The ID of the application that created the group DM. A value of 0 means this group wasn't created by an application.

      Bots shouldn't ever have this value being 0.
